featured_reviews.review_id:
Profoundly disappointing visit.  I called ahead, 2 hours before their closing time, to verify they were open and all was well.  What I wasn't told over the phone, however, would have changed my decision to visit.

I was only in the city for an evening, before traveling on to my next destination.  I took an Uber to Eastern Avenue Video, and as my ride pulled away and I entered the place, I was immediately told, "THE ARCADE IS CLOSED FOR MAINTENANCE, FEEL FREE TO BUY SOMETHING, THOUGH."

I said, "I just called to verify y'all were open.  Why didn't you mention the that the arcade was closed then?"  The female clerk replied "We ARE open, honey.  Now, you need to buy something but you can't just hang around, OK?"

I asked them if they could wait long enough for me to call another Uber (there was a gentleman also behind the counter, apparently a manager).  I was told that was OK.  Unfortunately, I had a very hard time getting an Uber to come back.  Ultimately, I had to walk about a half a mile toward the Omni Hotel, before my attempts to get a ride were accepted again.

I feel like the main failure here was, obviously, to tell a caller the facilities were open, but to not reveal that the arcade was closed.  This could have been an oversight, but it sure felt a lot like deceptive omission instead.  I will not attempt another visit if I'm in Oklahoma City again.

Son derece hayal kirikligi yaratan bir ziyaret. Acik olduklarini ve her seyin yolunda oldugunu dogrulamak icin kapanis saatinden 2 saat once aradim. Ancak telefonda bana soylenmeyenler ziyaret kararimi degistirebilirdi.

Bir sonraki hedefime dogru yola cikmadan once sehirde yalnizca bir aksam kaldim. Uber'den Eastern Avenue Video'ya bindim ve aracim uzaklasip mekana girdigimde hemen bana soyle soylendi: "APARIS BAKIM NEDENIYLE KAPALIDIR, AMA BIR SEY SATIN ALMAKTAN CEKINMEYIN."

"Hepinizin acik oldugunu dogrulamak icin aradim. O zaman neden atari salonunun kapali oldugundan bahsetmediniz?" dedim. Kadin tezgahtar cevapladi: "Kapimiz acik tatlim. Simdi bir seyler alman lazim ama oylece takilip kalamazsin, tamam mi?"

Onlara baska bir Uber'i aramam icin yeterince bekleyip bekleyemeyeceklerini sordum (tezgahin arkasinda da bir beyefendi vardi, gorunuse gore bir yoneticiydi). Bana bunun sorun olmadigi soylendi. Ne yazik ki Uber'in geri gelmesini saglamakta cok zorlandim. En sonunda, arabaya binme girisimlerim tekrar kabul edilinceye kadar Omni Otel'e dogru yarim mil kadar yurumek zorunda kaldim.

Buradaki asil basarisizligin, arayan kisiye tesislerin acik oldugunu soylemek ama oyun salonunun kapali oldugunu aciklamamak oldugunu dusunuyorum. Bu bir gozden kacirma olabilirdi, ama bunun yerine kesinlikle aldatici bir ihmal gibi geldi. Tekrar Oklahoma City'de olursam baska bir ziyarete kalkismayacagim.
